    "prerequisites": ["time-matrix-19"],
    "lesson_content_markdown": "# The Silver Boss Battle\n\nWelcome to the Silver Boss Battle! You have learned the complex sequences of the past and the objective voice of the academy. Now, it's time to put it all together.\n\n### 1. Review of Concepts\n- **Present Perfect**: *\"I have already seen it.\"* (Life experience or unfinished time.)\n- **Since vs. For**: *\"Since 2010\"* (start) vs. *\"For 10 years\"* (duration).\n- **Past Perfect**: *\"I had finished before he arrived.\"* (Earlier action.)\n- **Past Perfect Continuous**: *\"I had been working for hours.\"* (Duration before a past event.)\n- **Present & Past Passive**: *\"The test is shown / The test was shown.\"* (Focus on the object.)\n\n### 2. The Boss Strategy\n- **Check for Time Words**: Are there words like *yesterday*, *already*, or *by the time*?\n- **Check for Focus**: Is the focus on the **person** or the **object**?\n- **Check for Sequence**: Which event happened first in the past?\n---",
